<p t="478962" d="1869" wp="1" ws="1">and the word &quot;sponsored&quot; is good enough.</p>
<p t="480831" d="1338" wp="1" ws="1">The British regulators,</p>
<p t="482169" d="2679" wp="3" ws="1">of which there are three
