<p t="553245" d="3829" wp="1" ws="1">But that&#39;s a standard that doesn&#39;t
seem to apply to anyone else.</p>
<p t="560470" d="3273" wp="6" ws="1">This is gonna be a really difficult
video to make.</p>
<p t="563743" d="3222" wp="6" ws="1">There are a lot of people
I need to apologise to.</p>
